    fixSummary: '(1) Check V$SQL ORDER BY cpu_time for top CPU consumers. (2) If hard parses >100/s, fix bind variable usage (cursor_sharing=FORCE or app fix). (3) If buffer gets high, tune SQL access path. (4) Check parallel query degree — unintended parallelism multiplies CPU.',
